# âš™ï¸ 3ï¸âƒ£ APM / Backend Security Dashboard

This is the bridge between infrastructure and user experience.

Here you detect:

- Service instability
- API abuse
- Authentication attacks
- Backend failures

## ğŸ¯ Monitor

Operational:

